oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Variety Show at the Columbus Municipal Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Stringbean, 1915-1973; Pearl, Minnie;Wilburn Brothers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) Hatch poster announcing the Grand Ole Opry Variety show featuring Jim Reeves and the Blue Boys, Minnie Pearl, Flatt and Scruggs, the Wilburn Brothers, String bean, and Margie Bowes at the Municipal Auditorium on March 16. Poster features metal photoplates of Jim Reeves, Minnie Pearl, Flatt and Scruggs, the Wilburn Brothers, String bean, and Margie Bowes.
